> ...most of their activity will be devoted to the perpetuation of the organization, not to the pursuit of its ostensible objective.<p>aka, the tyranny of the bureaucratic overhead equation<p><pre><code>    Δw = p ln (st / sg)

    w  := &quot;useful work towards the objective&quot;
    g  := &quot;the group of people doing w&quot;
    p  := &quot;effective productivity of g&quot;
    sg := &quot;total size of the g&quot;
    st := &quot;total size of the organization (sg + bureaucracy)&quot;</code></pre>
